      "blocks": {
        "kids-review-1": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Perfect for My 3-Year-Old",
            "text": "<p>This toy is incredibly well-made and my toddler absolutely loves it. I feel confident knowing it meets all safety standards. It has held up amazingly well despite daily use!</p>",
            "author": "<em><strong>Amanda W.</strong></em>"
          }
        },
        "kids-review-2": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Educational and Fun",
            "text": "<p>My kids are learning through play and they don’t even realize it. The quality is outstanding and I love that the materials are completely non-toxic. A win for the whole family!</p>",
            "author": "<em><strong>Chris P.</strong></em>"
          }
        },
        "kids-review-3": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Great Quality",
            "text": "<p>This has exceeded all our expectations. The craftsmanship is superb and my children play with it for hours. So much better than the cheap alternatives we’ve tried before.</p>",
